ertain about how dropbox works, but theoretically if anyone links to that exact URL, then it would always be the latest version? Right now it's 1.0... It's not important in this case to keep record of earlier versions.</div> You got it. But I think I'm just going to remove the _release_latest suffix altogether since, like you said, previous revisions don't matter anyway.<br /><br />Update: SNES Schematic v1.1 is available here: <a href="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/36237540/SNES/jwdonal/schematics/snes_schematic.zip" class="postlink">https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/36237540/SNES/jwdonal/schematics/snes_schematic.zip</a>

		

